caption.text:
•I'm the light•
which too bright for your sight.
All the darks that ever matter to you, but still you embrace 'em with all your affection.
You did.
I saw it.
I'm not forget.
They ever became your lights too. 
It's okay I know it need a bless more than I could receive, and I'm sorry if this light wants to be a darkness.
Darkness, to distract your sight!
Darkness, so I can get your attention!
I'll be the darkness who cannot forget how it hurts being a light.
Darkness which too dark for your sight, again.
And left you die at the end.

Sept/3/2017 - few hours before my 2 years anniversary.
